<h2>Syllabus</h2>

This syllabus is tentative and subject to change. 

<ul>

<li>CPU virtualization: processes, scheduling</li>
<li>Memory virtualization: address spaces, translation, segmentation,
paging, swapping</li>
<li>Concurrency: threading, locks, condition variables,
semaphores</li>
<li>Persistence: RAID, file systems, journaling</li>
<li>(only if time permits) Security: authentication, access control,
cryptography</li>
</ul>


